column14: Man made trench cut through beaver dam to create discharge out of gauge pool. Measured below dam in line with trench. Only wide enough for single FT2 panel. Trench was 0.1m wide and 0.05m deep. Estimated 0.001m3/s discharge. DWL at arrival, HG has SRC, HG2 does not. Swapped HG and HG2 after 16:40. OTT is HG for 4:45, Amasser is HG2 for 16:45. Reset OTT (HG) and  Amasser (HG2) after swap, prior to 16:45 reading. Water level unchanged. Append HG2 (OTT) record prior to visit without any SRC. Then HG record from 16:45 onward is valid, no reset / SRC. Other Methods Estimated
